Fortis Healthcare Gains Ahead of Press Conference in New Delhi

-- B y   N i v e d i t h a   R a v i
-- 
2011-09-19T03:48:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/fortis-healthcare-gains-ahead-of-press-conference-in-new-delhi.html
Fortis Healthcare India Ltd. gained
2.5 percent to 150.8 rupees as of 9:16 a.m. in Mumbai. The
hospital operator will brief reporters today in  New Delhi  on a
strategic announcement, the company said in an e-mailed
statement on Sept. 17, without giving further details.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niveditha Ravi at 
 nravi2@bloomberg.net  